{"tid":2349072,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［邪不能勝正］強烈建議蕭正楠重歸香港樂壇！！！","createTime":"2021-01-01T09:05:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T09:44:12.000Z","uid":56716,"like":7,"dislike":89,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"40da638b4533d723ff26ccc00e58e3f881fff1e4","tid":2349072,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T09:05:42.000Z","msg":"蕭正楠外型唔差（幾靚仔，初出道被封為翻版鄭伊健），唱功唔錯（一定好過<span class=\"red\">邪</span>多多聲），無奈當日因一句說話令佢歌唱事業玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢首「接受我」係第一代兵仔歌，唱live絕對見得人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/h6HkPI1njSA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fh6HkPI1njSA&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gcF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=d9d2db40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/h6HkPI1njSA</a><br />\n<br />\n「Together」同「感激我遇見」，唱功比原唱讀歌王子鄭伊健穩定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gaHZhOaV1wc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgaHZhOaV1wc&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gcF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=f95e7972\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gaHZhOaV1wc</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aK_l4AGJLuY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaK_l4AGJLuY&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gcF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=18af5a4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aK_l4AGJLuY</a><br />\n<br />\n「男朋友」，呢個髮型仲似伊健<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ijsTq9N5e0I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FijsTq9N5e0I&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gcF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=ab48d184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ijsTq9N5e0I</a><br />\n<br />\n「夏日傾情」，冧爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LQOVNERlKY4\" data-sr-url=\